data.description: Bring your personal items and make this Ranch house located in Town Of Oneonta yours Today! Features include large living and dining room, built ins for plenty of storage, hardwood floors and all new kitchen appliances. Back handicap ramp leads to the the entrance of large family room complete with a propane stove for those chilly fall/winter days. Basement has a laundry room and large rec room with a  built in bar. Home is located on a quiet street with a well manicured yard and privacy, large 2 car garage and paved driveway. Make your appointment to see this lovely home today!
